OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FStephen King testifies     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fagainst publishing merger  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, American horror novelist Stephen King  
OL,6, is taking on a new monster: corporate  
OL,7, consolidation.                         
OL,9,FThe author was the star witness in an  
OL,10,Fanti-trust trial to block the two      
OL,11,Fbiggest US publishers' $2.2bn merger.  
OL,13,FThe US Department of Justice called on 
OL,14,FKing to testify about how the proposed 
OL,15,Ftie-up of Penguin Random House and     
OL,16,FSimon & Schuster could affect authors. 
OL,18,FKing, 75, told the court in Washington 
OL,19,FDC that he felt "the move would be bad 
OL,20,Ffor competition in the industry".      
